Package: bitscale
Type: Package
Title: Convert the theta scale of an item response theory (IRT) model into a bit scale
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Joakim", "Wallmark",
      email = "wallmark.joakim@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package converts the theta scale from an IRT model (fitted using the mirt package) into a bit scale.
    It implements the bit scale transformation as introduced by Wallmark et al. (2024).
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
    mirt,
    ggplot2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/joakimwallmark/bitscale
BugReports: https://github.com/joakimwallmark/bitscale/issues
